{"tid":2152494,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部副部長樂玉成批評美方無真憑實據下威脅禁TikTok","createTime":"2020-08-12T04:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T05:38:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"78bbe93beab3e620432eadd7514c85a8c9badea0","tid":2152494,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T04:28:59.000Z","msg":"外交部副部長樂玉成接受內地傳媒訪問說，中方沒有被美國宣布制裁中央與特區政府11名官員的事嚇倒，相反對有官員被列在美國的制裁名單上感到光榮，認為有關名單變成了一份「表揚名單」。<br />\n<br />\n樂玉成又說，美國政府對TikTok進行有罪推定，拿不出任何真憑實據下，威脅在45天內強制出售或禁用，是強盜邏輯，反問TikTok的錯在哪。他估計美國要將TikTok置於死地，唯一真實原因就是TikTok有中國血統，跟國家安全毫不相干，認為全世界都不齒美國巧取豪奪的行為。<br />\n<br />\n樂玉成認為，在涉及國家核心利益和民族尊嚴的問題上，中方無路可退。他形容，部分美國政客「逢中必反」，極力挑動中美意識形態對抗的「新冷戰」，不過，他已做好隨時與美方對話的準備。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543252-20200812.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543252-20200812.htm&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfyK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=3550e61c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543252-20200812.htm&h=a3664bdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543252-20200812.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4ff07fbc857377a3e2bfadb34543e28c569c3bfa","tid":2152494,"uid":21602,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T04:34:04.000Z","msg":"Facebook ig Gmail google map YouTube twitter WhatsApp Netflix: ......"},{"pid":"f73108d213be0f2196cf73bb74bb79ae6cde0fb9","tid":2152494,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T04:38:17.000Z","msg":"咁即係想真憑實據公諸於世，係咪?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e034c4d792dbc6df4abcc4bf4e30fe4a077da6e5","tid":2152494,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T05:24:07.000Z","msg":"你禁fb ig whatsapp有俾過理據咩？"},{"pid":"98baca8ada53f773dd74c5914c4edeafd9db49ca","tid":2152494,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":